                     <title xml:lang="he-Latn-x-lc">Mavo ha-ne῾arim</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <title xml:lang="he">מבוא הנערים</title>
                     
                     
                     
                     <note>
                        
                        
                        
                        <p>In the Hebrew translation of Avraham Avigdor (finished in 1379 in Montpellier). The work, a tract on fever, is divided into 6 chapters. </p>
                     
                     
                     
                     </note>
                     
                     
                     
                     <filiation>Cf. the contents of Add MS 27170. </filiation>
                  
                  
                  
